                            <p>The death rate in Mexico is something that worries me the most. It is higher than Poland
                                and continues in this same trend. I hope these doesn’t mean that we are neither not
                                treating well our patients or that based on our population characteristics we are less
                                stronger to the Coronavirus. </p>



